Starscram got up after his little incident. This was crazy! KitKat 
and him needed serious attention. They had no base. They had no 
supplies, and now the other Preds were trying to get them to join 
them. The old assimillation technique. We'd probably be made low 
ranking officers. And where was their all might leader Megatron at 
this time? Off chasing some unknown aliens whil his crew was getting 
blown to bits! Starscream looked from KitKat, to Tarantulas, and than 
to Drillbit.

"Look at her! She's in no position to be making command decisions! 
Look at the pain she's in!" Starscream looked at her caringly, "I 
think the damage might be much worse than I thought. She might have 
broken a big vital system inside her body. If we don't get help soon 
she might die. One of us has to relieve her of command."
